<div class="row">
  <div class="large-12 columns">
    <h2>Our Approach</h2>
    <p class="subheader"> At CM Suby, we understand that redesigning a home can be stressful to your daily routine. Your home is important to you and we take all the necessary precautions to ensure a successful project. Check below for a look into a typical bathroom renovation.</p>

    <div id='container1' div class="twentytwenty-container">
      <img alt="Sample before" src="/images/approach/bathroom_before.png"/>
      <img alt="Sample after" src="/images/approach/bathroom_after.png"/>
    </div>

    <hr class="style-two">
    <div class="row" data-equalizer>
      <div class="medium-4 large-4 columns">
        <ul class="pricing-table" data-equalizer-watch>
          <li class="title">Phase 1</li>
          <li class="price">Pre-work</li>
          <li class="bullet-item">Apply for all necessary permits</li>
          <li class="bullet-item">Protect the house</li>
          <li class="bullet-item">Gut and remove material off premises</li>
          <li class="bullet-item">Rebuild area according to blueprints/drawings.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="medium-4 large-4 columns">
        <ul class="pricing-table" data-equalizer-watch>
          <li class="title">Phase 2</li>
          <li class="price">Construction</li>
          <li class="bullet-item">Rough electrical or electrical upgrades, if necessary</li>
          <li class="bullet-item">Set up rough inspections for plumbing, building and electrical</li>
          <li class="bullet-item">Insulation upgrade/insulation inspection</li>
          <li class="bullet-item">Sheetrock/tape/spackle (3 coats)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="medium-4 large-4 columns">
        <ul class="pricing-table" data-equalizer-watch>
          <li class="title">Phase 3</li>
          <li class="price">Final Touches</li>
          <li class="bullet-item">Tile installation/grout</li>
          <li class="bullet-item">Trim work /trim out fixtures plumbing/electrical</li>
          <li class="bullet-item">Final measurements for shower or tub door</li>
          <li class="bullet-item">When completed final inspections scheduled (plumbing-building-electrical)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

